**/*.secret
# .serena/ (below) already blanket-ignores this, so no per-file rule needed —
# REDACTED 2026-0x: .serena/memories/woocommerce_api_credentials.md once held
# a live WooCommerce secret. The file is deleted and the directory is
# ignored either way, but ROTATION STATUS OF THAT KEY IS UNCONFIRMED — this
# comment does not prove the key was rotated. Verify before trusting it's dead.

# --- Claude Code ---
# agents/skills/hooks/workflows/state are source, tracked (128 files already
# were, force-added ad hoc — this makes it structural instead of manual).
# Only genuinely personal/ephemeral/generated pieces stay local.
.claude/settings.local.json
.claude/settings.json.bak
.claude/settings.json.bak.*
.claude/settings.json.backup-*
.claude/settings.json.audit-bak-*
.claude/settings.json.pre-agent-fix-*
.claude/agent-state/
.claude/worktrees/
.claude/scheduled_tasks.lock
.claude/tidy-log.jsonl

